(-a)\cdot (-x)=ax
b=-a
 bx + b(-x) = b(x+(-x)) = b\cdot 0 = 0 \Rightarrow b(-x) = -(bx) 
(-a)(-x)  + (-ax) = (-a)(-x) + (-a)x = (-a) [ (-x) + x] = (-a)( x + (-x) ) = (-a) 0 = 0 
\alpha : A \to B
\alpha(a+a')=\alpha(a)+\alpha(a')
\alpha(0)=0
a=a'=0
\alpha(-a)=- \alpha(a)
a'=-a
\alpha(0)=0
\beta : A \times A' \to B
A \times A \to A
\beta(-a,-x)=- \beta(a,-x)=- - \beta(a,x) = \beta(a,x)
